  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220514527769\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220514527769\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>일주일에 꼭 두번씩 오셔서 치료받으시는 환자분께서</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>저번주에는 여행을 가신다고 안오시고,</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>오늘 다시 내원하셨는데</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>양손에 짐을 이렇게나 많이 들고오셨다</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>\"선생님.. 이거.. 저번주에 제주도 다녀오면서 사왔어요..</span><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>\"</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>\"아 네.. 고맙습니다.. 뭘 요런걸 사오셨어요 그냥오셔도되는데 ^^</span><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>\"</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>\"요건 원장님꺼..\"</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>\"네 ㅎㅎ 빵 잘먹겠습니다! 고맙습니다~\"</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151020_146/isuhani_1445328349897lQy1G_JPEG/PA204839.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151020_146/isuhani_1445328349897lQy1G_JPEG/PA204839.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003357B0AA19')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151020_146/isuhani_1445328349897lQy1G_JPEG/PA204839.JPG?type=w3\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_characters_in_love\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/line_characters_in_love/original_31.png?type=p50_50\" width=\"164\" height=\"151\" style=\"border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 164px; height: 151px;\" alt=\"line_characters_in_love-31\"></a><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></div></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151020_181/isuhani_1445328304547yj0x1_JPEG/PA204842.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151020_181/isuhani_1445328304547yj0x1_JPEG/PA204842.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003357B0AA19')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151020_181/isuhani_1445328304547yj0x1_JPEG/PA204842.JPG?type=w3\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>이건 Terarosa Coffee라고 원장님꺼용~ </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>흠.. 검색창에 \"제주도 테라로사\"라고 검색을 해보니</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>멋있게 잘해놨네요</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>분위기 있어보여요 ㅎ</span><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>저두 나중에 제주도 가면 꼭 한번 들려봐야겠어요</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151020_241/isuhani_1445328305240c7typ_JPEG/PA204841.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151020_241/isuhani_1445328305240c7typ_JPEG/PA204841.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003357B0AA19')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151020_241/isuhani_1445328305240c7typ_JPEG/PA204841.JPG?type=w3\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>미니 식빵</span><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151020_171/isuhani_1445328305523qawaB_JPEG/PA204840.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151020_171/isuhani_1445328305523qawaB_JPEG/PA204840.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003357B0AA19')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151020_171/isuhani_1445328305523qawaB_JPEG/PA204840.JPG?type=w3\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>핸드메이드 잼</span><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151020_179/isuhani_1445328305732qAwrl_JPEG/PA204843.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151020_179/isuhani_1445328305732qAwrl_JPEG/PA204843.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003357B0AA19')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151020_179/isuhani_1445328305732qAwrl_JPEG/PA204843.JPG?type=w3\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>잼은 두가지 맛이에요</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151020_61/isuhani_1445328305977RVaMV_JPEG/PA204846.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151020_61/isuhani_1445328305977RVaMV_JPEG/PA204846.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003357B0AA19')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151020_61/isuhani_1445328305977RVaMV_JPEG/PA204846.JPG?type=w3\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>하나는 홍차 &amp; 밀크잼</span><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151020_83/isuhani_1445328306149CK2Pc_JPEG/PA204847.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151020_83/isuhani_1445328306149CK2Pc_JPEG/PA204847.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003357B0AA19')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151020_83/isuhani_1445328306149CK2Pc_JPEG/PA204847.JPG?type=w3\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>하나는 레드향 마말레이드</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151020_77/isuhani_1445328306342w4Ar7_JPEG/PA204848.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151020_77/isuhani_1445328306342w4Ar7_JPEG/PA204848.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003357B0AA19')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151020_77/isuhani_1445328306342w4Ar7_JPEG/PA204848.JPG?type=w3\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>두가지 다 맛있는데,</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>저는 개인적으로 홍차&amp;밀크잼이 더 맛있네요 ㅋㅋ</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>그냥 수저로 막 떠먹고싶은? ㅎㅎ</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>병도이쁘고 포장도 이쁘고 맛도 좋고</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>무엇보다 선물해주신 환자분은 더 좋다요!</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>마음씨도 이쁘고 따뜻하구..</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>같은 한국이지만 그래도 먼 타지까지 가셔서</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>우리 한의원 식구들까지 챙겨주시고... ㅠㅠ</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>그동안 에그타르트랑 통밀빵도 사주시고.. </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>매번 '감사합니다' 라는 말&nbsp;밖에 드릴수 없는 제맘이 참.. </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&#8203;ㅠㅠ</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'><br /></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>진짜 천사 같은 우리 환자분.. </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>항상 건강하세요! ^^ </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_characters_in_love\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/line_characters_in_love/original_1.png?type=p50_50\" alt=\"line_characters_in_love-1\"></a>&#8203;</span><span style='font-family: \"3028108_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span></p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
